txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Blackened filth from the lesser insects, spiders, and Neekerbreekers found throughout Bree-land. Deliver the items to Second-watcher Heathstraw at the Boar Fountain in Bree.
'I would say that this is an accurately described sample. Thank you.'
'Seems an awful request of an object, but I am told by those who posted the duty that the filth can be used. If you are willing, then the people of Bree would be grateful.'
Men of Bree Task: Blackened Filth
Second-watcher Heathstraw is offering compensation for the collection of blackened filth from insects, spiders, and Neekerbreekers throughout Bree-land.
Deliver the blackened filth to Second-watcher Heathstraw

You have been tasked with finding blackened filth from the weaker insects, spiders, and Neekerbreekers making Bree-land their home. Second-watcher Heathstraw awaits the delivery of these items at the Boar Fountain in Bree.
Wanted: Blackened filth from the lesser insects, spiders, and Neekerbreekers found throughout Bree-land.
